2Fross-taylor-says-india-will-be-nervous-facing-new-zealand-as-mind-games-come-into-play-ahead-of-world-cup-semis%2Farticleshow%2F105188010.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20be%20nervous%20facing%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20reckons%20Ross%20Taylor%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20from%20the%20campaigns%20of%20both%20teams%20in%20the%202019%20edition.%20New%20Zealand%20had%20stopped%20India's%20dominant%20run%20four%20years%20ago%20when%20they%20beat%20the%20Virat%20Kohli-led%20side%20in%20the%20rain-hit%20semifinal%20at%20Manchester.%20Like%202019%2C%20India%20go%20into%20the%20semifinals%20as%20table%20toppers.%20New%20Zealand%2C%20who%20started%20the%20tournament%20well%2C%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20with%20five%20wins%20in%20nine%20games.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elite%20investor%20Jim%20Rogers%20touts%20gold%20and%20silver%20over%20stocks%20and%20real%20estate%20-%20and%20warns%20inflation%20will%20worsen%20and%20a%20recession%20is%20looming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223966%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jim%20Rogers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5efe077c5af6cc7e317b5ca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221983%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJim%20Rogers.%3Cp%3ESergei%20Savostyanov%2FTASS%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGold%20and%20silver%20are%20better%20bets%20than%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20or%20real%20estate%20right%20now%2C%20Jim%20Rogers%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGeorge%20Soros'%20former%20business%20partner%20said%20commodities%20tend%20to%20do%20well%20during%20inflationary%20periods.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERogers%20expects%20inflation%20to%20worsen%20again%2C%20and%20sees%20a%20recession%20as%20almost%20inevitable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJim%20Rogers%20expects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price%5C%22%3Egold%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fsilver-price%5C%22%3Esilver%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20outshine%20other%20assets%20during%20a%20period%20of%20historic%20inflation%20and%20widespread%20worry%20about%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20a%20world%20where%20prices%20are%20going%20higher%2C%20you%20want%20to%20own%20the%20things%20that%20are%20going%20higher%20in%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20investor%20told%20%26quot%3BThe%20Julia%20La%20Roche%20Show%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQv4zNqvT9q0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERogers%20is%20best%20known%20as%20George%20Soros'%20former%20business%20partner%2C%20and%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Quantum%20Fund%20and%20Soros%20Fund%20Management.%20He%20explained%20that%20fast-rising%20prices%20make%20fixed-income%20assets%20like%20bonds%20less%20attractive%2C%20and%20the%20higher%20interest%20rates%20that%20typically%20accompany%20them%20often%20weigh%20on%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20real-estate%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20commodities%20like%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20rice%20tend%20to%20appreciate%20during%20inflationary%20times%2C%20meaning%20they're%20%26quot%3Busually%20a%20good%20place%20to%20ride%20it%20out%20and%20even%20perhaps%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20said.%20He%20singled%20out%20gold%20as%20a%20historical%20beneficiary%20of%20surging%20prices%20and%20raging%20wars%2C%20but%20hailed%20silver%20as%20the%20better%20bet%20today%20as%20its%20price%20is%20much%20more%20depressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERogers%20also%20said%20he%20expects%20other%20currencies%20to%20threaten%20the%20US%20dollar's%20role%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%2C%20but%20he%20hasn't%20found%20the%20likely%20winner%20from%20de-dollarization%20as%20yet.%20He%20noted%20that%20Washington's%20use%20of%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20over%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20has%20stoked%20concerns%20in%20several%20nations%20that%20the%20dollar%20isn't%20a%20neutral%20haven%2C%20and%20could%20become%20a%20liability%20if%20a%20country%20angers%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAdventure%20Capitalist%3A%20The%20Ultimate%20Road%20Trip%26quot%3B%20also%20rang%20the%20inflation%20alarm.%20Price%20growth%20has%20slowed%20from%20a%2040-year%20high%20of%20over%209%25%20last%20summer%20to%20below%204%25%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20but%20it%20has%20remained%20well%20above%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20target%20of%202%25%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20staggering%20amounts%20of%20money%20printing%20in%20the%20last%20year%20or%20two%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20worse%20inflation%2C%20it's%20not%20over%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20all%20going%20to%20pay%20the%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERogers%20said%20that%20governments%20would%20print%20money%20aggressively%20once%20their%20economies%20show%20signs%20of%20slowing%2C%20refueling%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20expect%20an%20imminent%20recession%20given%20the%20amount%20of%20government%20spending%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20the%20likelihood%20that%20politicians%20will%20shore%20up%20the%20economy%20ahead%20of%20a%20presidential%20election%20this%20year.%20But%20a%20major%20downturn%20seems%20virtually%20assured%20at%20this%20point%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20it%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20a%20recession.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20getting%20closer%2C%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20happen%20but%20it%20always%20has%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20longest%20period%20without%20a%20recession%20in%20American%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-rogers-gold-silver-stocks-bonds-real-estate-inflation-recession-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699881942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5efe078e3ad8611ad84f5fef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fjim-rogers-gold-silver-stocks-bonds-real-estate-inflation-recession-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rogers%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20George%20Soros'%20Quantum%20Fund%2C%20sees%20commodities%20as%20the%20best%20option%20for%20investors%20if%20inflation%20reaccelerates%20as%20he%20expects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fjim-rogers-gold-silver-stocks-bonds-real-estate-inflation-recession-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiger%203%20worldwide%20box%20office%20day%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699881812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105188619%2Cimgsize-28824.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Ftiger-3-worldwide-box-office-collection-day-1-the-salman-khan-katrina-kaif-and-emraan-hashmi-starrer-mints-rs-94-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105188619.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105188619.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan's%20latest%20film%2C%20%26quot%3BTiger%203%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20had%20a%20successful%20opening%20day%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20earning%20Rs%2094%20crore%20worldwide.%20The%20film%20has%20broken%20several%20records%2C%20including%20the%20high