nterview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Khaitan%2C%20who%20is%20professor%20of%20public%20law%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20presented%20an%20analytical%20framework%20for%20studying%20when%20a%20democracy%20is%20in%20peril.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comprises%20three%20elements%20to%20do%20with%20how%20accountable%20is%20the%20executive.%20First%2C%20its%20accountability%20to%20the%20people.%20Second%2C%20its%20accountability%20to%20other%20state%20institutions%20like%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20judiciary.%20Third%2C%20its%20accountability%20to%20the%20media%2C%20academic%20criticism%20and%20civil%20society%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Khaitan%20said%20this%20framework%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfair%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20power%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20aims%20to%20distinguish%20policies%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20framework%20and%20not%20their%20ideology.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20discussed%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20be%20accountable%20in%20each%20of%20the%20three%20respects%20that%20make%20up%20his%20analytical%20framework%2C%20i.e.%20to%20the%20people%2C%20to%20state%20institutions%20and%20to%20the%20media%20and%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20first%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20deliberate%20assault%20on%20democracy%20was%20corroborated%20and%20enhanced%20by%20the%20way%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20political%20opposition%20was%20constrained%2C%20especially%20by%20targeting%20the%20offices%20and%20institutions%20in%20which%20it%20still%20held%20sway%20(such%20as%20the%20upper%20chamber%20in%20the%20federal%20parliament%2C%20state%20governments%20it%20controlled%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition).%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20it%20was%20also%20permitted%20by%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cdesign%20flaws%20in%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20assault%20on%20Indian%20democracy%20compares%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Emergency%20of%201975%2C%20he%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20less%20upfront%20and%20more%20insidious.%20It%20creates%20fear%2C%20which%20often%20leads%20to%20people%20self-censoring%20their%20actions.%20This%20applies%20particularly%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20second%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20its%20Hindutva%2FHindu%20Rashtra%20agenda.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20very%20close%20to%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20if%20it%20has%20not%20already%20been%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Rashtra%20is%20already%20here%20and%20only%20its%20formal%20announcement%20is%20awaited.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20is%20not%20simply%20imperiling%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20but%20%E2%80%9Credefining%20who%20we%20are%20as%20a%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsLRO4qs6Q-Q%3Fsi%3DfNsmFaA9IbXvgJwF%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699878609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F13174732%2FKT-13-Nov-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fthe-modi-govt-is-guilty-of-killing-the-constitution-by-a-1000-cuts-says-lse-professor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Professor%20Tarunabh%20Khaitan%20told%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20many%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20parties%20and%20institutions%20have%20%E2%80%9Csleepwalked%20into%20(Modi%E2%80%99s)%20authoritarianism%E2%80%9D%20while%20others%20%E2%80%9Care%20complicit