y%20and%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Journal%20of%20Controversial%20Ideas%2C%20shared%20the%20study%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20article%20challenges%20societal%20%26quot%3Btaboos%26quot%3B%20surrounding%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20activities%20with%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20thought-provoking%20article%20is%20'Zoophilia%20Is%20Morally%20Permissible'%20by%20Fira%20Bensto%20(pseudonym)%2C%20which%20is%20just%20out%20in%20the%20current%20issue%20of%20%5Bthe%20Journal%20of%20Controversial%20Ideas%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Singer%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20piece%20challenges%20one%20of%20society's%20strongest%20taboos%20and%20argues%20for%20the%20moral%20permissibility%20of%20some%20forms%20of%20sexual%20contact%20between%20humans%20and%20animals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20article%20offers%20a%20controversial%20perspective%20that%20calls%20for%20a%20serious%20and%20open%20discussion%20on%20animal%20ethics%20and%20sex%20ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Princeton%20University%20bioethics%20professor%20added%2C%20encouraging%20people%20to%20%26quot%3Bread%20and%20ponder%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20promoting%20sex%20with%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnother%20thought-provoking%20article%20is%20%26quot%3BZoophilia%20Is%20Morally%20Permissible%26quot%3B%20by%20Fira%20Bensto%20(pseudonym)%2C%20which%20is%20just%20out%20in%20the%20current%20issue%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJConIdeas%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40JConIdeas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20piece%20challenges%20one%20of%20society's%20strongest%20taboos%20and%20argues%20for%20the%20moral%20permissibility%20of%20some%20forms%20of%20sexual%E2%80%A6%20%3