5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105185142.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Polish%20parliament%20is%20convening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20last%20month's%20election%2C%20marking%20a%20change%20in%20direction%20for%20Poland%20amidst%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%20President%20Andrzej%20Duda%20will%20open%20the%20session%2C%20with%20lawmakers%20taking%20their%20oaths%20and%20electing%20a%20speaker.%20Outgoing%20Prime%20Minister%20Mateusz%20Morawiecki%20is%20expected%20to%20remain%20as%20caretaker%20premier%20while%20a%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%20The%20winning%20alliance%20aims%20to%20repair%20foreign%20alliances%20and%20restore%20democratic%20norms%20after%20years%20of%20conflict%20with%20the%20EU.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolands-newly-elected-parliament-meets-for-the-first-time%2Farticleshow%2F105185142.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolands-newly-elected-parliament-meets-for-the-first-time%2Famp_articleshow%2F105185142.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpolands-newly-elected-parliament-meets-for-the-first-time%2Famp_articleshow%2F105185142.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Gives%20New%20Role%20To%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Amid%20Ethics%20Panel%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20district%20chief%20of%20Krishnanagar%20(Nadia%20North)%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20Ms%20Moitra%20got%20the%20new%20role%20in%20the%20party%20led%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20amid%20a%20huge%20controversy%20in%20the%20cash-for-query%20case%20against%20the%20Bengal%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20thanked%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20party%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20AITC%20(All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress)%20for%20appointing%20me%20district%20president%20of%20Krishnanagar%20(Nadia%20North).%20Will%20always%20work%20with%20the%20party%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Krishnanagar%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMamataOfficial%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MamataOfficial%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAITCofficial%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AITCofficial%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20appointing%20me%20District%20President%20of%20Krishnanagar%20(Nadia%20North)%20.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWill%20always%20work%20with%20the%20party%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Krishnanagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mahua%20Moitra%20(%40MahuaMoitra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMahuaMoitra%2Fstatus%2F1723999967369740476%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20is%20among%2015%20other%20new%20district%20chiefs%20announced%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20Bengal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20closely%20watching%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20cash-for-query%20case%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20without%20wading%20into%20publicly%20defending%20her.%20The%20party%20has%20been%20circumspect%20in%20taking%20a%20public%20position%2C%20though%20Trinamool%20MP%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20supported%20her%20over%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20ethics%20committee%20to%20recommend%20her%20suspension%20from%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20move%20to%20give%20her%20charge%20of%20a%20district%20in%20her%20own%20constituency%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20indication%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20considers%20her%20one%20of%20their%20most%20important%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%2C%20after%20hearing%20Ms%20Moitra%20in%20a%20closed-door%20meeting%20from%20which%20she%20and%20opposition%20MPs%20walked%20out%20over%20the%20manner%20of%20questioning%2C%20in%20its%20500-page%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20said%20she%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20as%20an%20MP%20and%20her%20membership%20should%20be%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20called%20Ms%20Moitra's%20actions%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20objectionable%2C%20unethical%2C%20heinous%20and%20criminal%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20sought%20severe%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20500-page%20report%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Blegal%2C%20intensive%2C%20institutional%20and%20time-bound%20investigation%26quot%3B%20be%20held%20into%20the%20entire%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20concluded%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20shared%20user%20ID%20with%20%26quot%3Bunauthorised%20persons%26quot%3B%2C%20took%20cash%20and%20amenities%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20and%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20misdemeanour%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20part%20which%20calls%20for%20%26quot%3Bserious%20punishment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20trail%20of%20cash%20transaction%20between%20Smt%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20Shri%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20'quid%20pro%20quo'%20should%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%20a%20legal%2C%20institutional%20and%20time-bound%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20-%20who%20had%20flagged%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20--%20has%20said%20the%20anti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20had%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20accepted%20cash%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%20on%20his%20behalf%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20business%20rival%20Adani%20Group.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20by%20sharing%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20with%20the%20businessman%2C%20has%20compromised%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20had%20admitted%20to%20it%2C%20but%20claimed%20there%20is%20no%20regulation%20governing%20sharing%20of%20login%20and%20password.%20Ahead%20of%20her%20hearing%20with%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20she%20had%20written%20them%20a%20letter%2C%20questioning%20%26quot%3BWhy%20these%20rules%20are%20not%20shared%20with%20MPs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699872300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fptunpgqo_mahua-moitra-pti_625x300_28_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-gives-new-role-to-mahua-moitra-amid-ethics-panel-probe-4570340%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20district%20chief%20of%20Krishnanagar%20(Nadia%20North)%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-gives-new-role-to-mahua-moitra-amid-ethics-panel-probe-4570340%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-gives-new-role-to-mahua-moitra-amid-ethics-panel-probe-4570340%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-gives-new-role-to-mahua-moitra-amid-ethics-panel-probe-4570340%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toddler%20a