%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDino%20Cantelmi%2C%20Randi%20Goldstein-Casey%2C%20and%20Elizabeth%20Fournier.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dino%20Cantelmi%2C%20Randi%20Goldstein-Casey%2C%20and%20Elizabeth%20Fournier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFunerals%20can%20be%20emotional%20and%20difficult%2C%20but%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20make%20them%20less%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFuneral%20directors%20suggest%20the%20family%20of%20the%20deceased%20set%20boundaries%20on%20interactions%20with%20guests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20guest%2C%20be%20respectful%20of%20the%20funeral%20home%20and%20the%20family%2C%20and%20dress%20appropriately.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20loved%20one%20dies%2C%20not%20only%20are%20you%20coping%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20someone%20who%20meant%20a%20great%20deal%20to%20you%2C%20but%20you%20might%20find%20yourself%20overwhelmed%20with%20a%20range%20of%20emotions%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappify-graphic-on-grief-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanger%20and%20sadness%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there%20could%20be%20a%20long%20to-do%20list%2C%20from%20notifying%20other%20people%20about%20the%20news%20to%20planning%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuneral-home-planning-service-going-out-in-style-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edetails%20for%20the%20funeral%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20never%20been%20to%20a%20funeral%2C%20or%20been%20in%20charge%20of%20planning%20one%2C%20it%20may%20be%20confusing%20to%20know%20what%20to%20do%20or%20what%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20asked%20funeral%20directors%20to%20share%20their%20top%20etiquette%20rules%20and%20common%20pet%20peeves%20that%20they%20wish%20more%20people%20knew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Come%20to%20the%20funeral%20home%20as%20prepared%20as%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20charge%20of%20planning%20the%20funeral%20arrangements%2C%20you%20may%20not%20know%20what%20you%20need%20to%20have%20with%20you%20to%20get%20the%20process%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldsteinsfuneral.com%2Fteam-member%2Frandi-goldstein-casey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERandi%20Goldstein-Casey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20and%20funeral%20director%20for%20Goldsteins'%20Rosenberg's%20Raphael-Sacks%20Funeral%20Home%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20recommends%20gathering%20a%20checklist%20of%20items%20before%20your%20first%20meeting%20with%20a%20funeral%20home%20and%20having%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20you%20want%20to%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERequired%20information%20includes%20the%20deceased's%20Social%20Security%20number%2C%20birth%20date%2C%20and%20parents'%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20funeral%20cannot%20take%20place%20without%20this%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Casey%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20said%20that%20it's%20important%20for%20families%20to%20understand%20there's%20nothing%20the%20funeral%20home%20can%20do%20without%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Keep%20the%20family%20room%20private%20before%20the%20funeral%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOftentimes%2C%20the%20close%20family%20will%20wait%20in%20a%20private%20room%20together%20before%20the%20funeral.%20As%20the%20guests%20arrive%20and%20get%20seated%20in%20the%20main%20room%2C%20Casey%20often%20witnesses%20a%20situation%20that%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20Casey%20sees%20guests%20trying%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20family's%20private%20room%20to%20see%20them%20before%20the%20funeral.%20While%20their%20intentions%20may%20be%20right%20%E2%80%94%20they%20want%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20and%20say%20hello%20%E2%80%94%20she%20recommends%20that%20families%20set%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20said%20guests%20should%20assume%20it%20isn't%20appropriate%20to%20visit%20the%20private%20family%20room%20before%20the%20funeral%20unless%20the%20family%20has%20said%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20the%20family's%20responsibility%20to%20entertain%20additional%20people%20during%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20a%20receiving%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20funeral%2C%20the%20close%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20loved%20one%20who%20died%20may%20feel%20pressure%20to%20spend%20quality%20time%20with%20the%20guests.%20Casey%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20set%20boundaries%20here%2C%20even%20if%20that%20means%20limiting%20time%20spent%20with%20those%20at%20the%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20families%20will%20do%20a%20receiving%20line%20at%20the%20funeral%20where%20each%20guest%20can%20approach%20them%2C%20Casey%20said%20doing%20so%20isn't%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%2C%20it%20is%20too%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20their%20composure%20to%20get%20through%20the%20funeral%2C%20yet%20alone%20a%20receiving%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20recommended%20that%20those%20in%20mourning%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20choose%20whom%20they%20want%20to%20speak%20to%20and%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Respect%20the%20funeral%20and%20the%20funeral%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cantelmifuneralhome.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDino%20Cantelmi%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20director%20of%20Cantelmi%20Funeral%20Home%20in%20Bethlehem%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20says%20there%20are%20a%20few%20rules%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20if%20you've%20never%20been%20to%20a%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Cantelmi%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20on%20time.%20Being%20late%2C%20he%20said%2C%20not%20only%20is%20disruptive%20to%20the%20service%20but%20is%20also%20disrespectful%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Cantelmi%20also%20said%20to%20try%20to%20dress%20appropriately.%20If%20the%20family%20doesn't%20provide%20a%20dress%20code%2C%20he%20recommends%20avoiding%20loungewear%20or%20looking%20sloppy%20and%20opting%20for%20business-type%20clothing%20that's%20respectful%20and%20conservative.%20He%20also%20said%20to%20avoid%20wearing%20bright%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20wearing%20black%20is%20not%20required%2C%20black%20is%20standard%20for%20people%20to%20wear%20at%20funerals%20and%20viewings%20because%20it%20symbolizes%20mourning%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20deceased%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Leave%20your%20phone%20in%20the%20car%20or%20in%20your%20pocket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20entering%20a%20funeral%2C%20Cantelmi%20said%2C%20one%20thing%20people%20can%20do%20is%20be%20aware%20of%20their%20cellphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20times%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20funeral%20service%2C%20someone's%20cellphone%20will%20ring%20very%20loudly%2C%20disrupting%20the%20service%2C%20and%20sometimes%20the%20person%20will%20answer%20the%20phone%20and%20hold%20a%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20possible%2C%20leave%20your%20phone%20in%20your%20car%2C%20but%20if%20you%20forget%2C%20Cantelmi%20said%2C%20keep%20it%20in%20your%20pocket%2C%20remembering%20to%20turn%20it%20on%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20any%20cellphone%20disruptions%2C%20he%20also%20said%20your%20funeral%20director%20could%20make%20an%20announcement%20before%20the%20service%20about%20silencing%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Assign%20someone%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20family%20drama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFunerals%20can%20bring%20together%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20who%20may%20not%20have%20been%20in%20the%20same%20room%20for%20many%20years.%20Some%20attendees%20may%20not%20get%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20so%20many%20times%20that%20a%20family%20member%20has%20asked%20me%20to%20not%20let%20certain%20people%20into%20a%20funeral%2C%26quot%3B%20Cantelmi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20when%20the%20funeral%20is%20public%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20tell%20someone%20they%20can't%20come%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20know%20that%20some%20prospective%20attendees%20don't%20get%20along%2C%20Cantelmi%20suggested%20having%20a%20plan%2C%20such%20as%20hiring%20a%20security%20detail%2C%20keeping%20the%20funeral%20details%20private%20to%20close%20family%20members%2C%20or%20assigning%20a%20family%20member%20the%20job%20of%20mitigating%20drama%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Lean%20on%20your%20funeral%20director%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20planning%20a%20funeral%2C%20you%20may%20find%20yourself%20with%20endless%20questions%20about%20a%20process%20that's%20personal%20and%20filled%20with%20emotions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cornerstonefuneral.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElizabeth%20Fournier%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20funeral%20director%20at%20Cornerstone%20Funeral%20Services%20in%20Boring%2C%20Oregon%2C%20said%20she%20wished%20more%20families%20knew%20that%20they%20could%20lean%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeath-care-workers-and-funeral-directors-collect-bodies-coronavirus-pandemic-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efuneral%20directors%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20funeral-home%20employees%20throughout%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFournier%20noted%20that%20most%20people%20don't%20go%20through%20this%20process%20often%2C%20saying%20they%20might%20need%20something%20explained%20to%20them%20and%20could%20feel%20alone%20in%20finding%20those%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20funeral%20directors%20and%20grief%20counselors%2C%20or%20religious%20advisors%2C%20are%20here%20to%20lift%20some%20of%20the%20burden%20off%20a%20family%20by%20providing%20options%2C%20correct%20information%2C%20and%20reliable%20resources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuneral-etiquette-rules-funeral-directors-wish-you-knew-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699870201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65517b9936d588dc55cf25e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuneral-etiquette-rules-funeral-directors-wish-you-knew-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Funeral%20directors%20share%20what%20not%20to%20do%20at%20funeral%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20burden%20the%20family%20of%20the%20deceased%20or%20cause%20a%20disturbance%20in%20the%20funeral%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuneral-etiquette-rules-funeral-directors-wish-you-knew-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tea%20and%20nickel%20on%20the%20agenda%20as%20Biden%20hosts%20Indonesian%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699870135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105184491%2Cimgsize-28324.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftea-and-nickel-on-the-agenda-as-biden-hosts-indonesian-president%2Farticleshow%2F105184243.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105184243.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20meet%20with%20Indonesian%20President%20Joko%20Widodo%20at%20the%20White%20House%20t