erson%20filming%20the%20video.%20A%20few%20other%20men%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20background%20but%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20any%20of%20them%20are%20among%20the%20arrested%20or%20accused.%C2%A0%26quot%3BSee%20what%20they%20did%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20tears%2C%20pointing%20to%20torn%20and%20stained%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20then%20repeatedly%20hits%20her%20head%20and%20grabs%20her%20hair%20to%20show%20how%20she%20was%20assaulted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20voice%20offscreen%20then%20asks%20if%20she%20can%20name%20her%20assaulters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20responds%2C%20%26quot%3BRitu...%20Riya...%20Lalita...%20Sonu...%20Vikram.%20Lock%20them%20all%20up.%20They%20are%20all%20in%20the%20sex%20work...%20they%20called%20me%20and%20they%20are%20blackmailing%20me.%26quot%3B%20In%20another%2C%20and%20more%20disturbing%2C%20video%2C%20the%20woman%20is%20being%20dragged%20out%20of%20a%20room%20by%20an%20unknown%20man%2C%20who%20also%20tried%20to%20cover%20her%20mouth%20as%20she%20screamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20an%20employee%20of%20a%20guest%20house%20and%20had%20been%20working%20there%20for%20nearly%2018%20months.%20She%20told%20police%20she%20had%20been%20pushed%20to%20engage%20in%20sex%20work%20in%20return%20for%20more%20money%20and%2C%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20had%20been%20told%20to%20come%20to%20the%20guest%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20then%20reportedly%20forced%20into%20sex%20acts%20against%20her%20will.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20after%20this%2C%20and%20as%20she%20was%20leaving%2C%20the%20guest%20house%20owners%20reportedly%20ordered%20her%20to%20stay%20the%20night.%20She%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20beaten%2C%20and%20hit%20with%20a%20beer%20bottle%2C%20when%20she%20refused.%20The%20assault%20and%20her%20screams%20led%20to%20a%20ruckus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20narrated%20the%20whole%20incident%20to%20us%20about%20bein