7%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bvoluntary%20resignation%26quot%3B%20package%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20fall%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Amazon%20was%20tracking%20and%20sharing%20individual%20office%20attendance%20records.%20Amazon%20also%20reportedly%20told%20managers%20that%20they%20can%20fire%20employees%20who%20don't%20adhere%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-lets-managers-terminate-employees-return-to-office-2023-10%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20times%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Amazon%20still%20features%20a%20remote%20jobs%20page%20on%20its%20AmazonJobs%20website%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BAmazon%20has%20virtual%20(or%20%26quot%3Bremote%26quot%3B)%20positions%20available%20to%20qualified%20individuals%20who%20live%20in%20some%20areas.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20says%20that%20remote%20work%20can%20be%20discussed%20with%20a%20recruiter%20during%20the%20interview%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20does%20Amazon%20pay%20to%20work%20from%20home%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESalaries%20at%20Amazon%20vary%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20role.%20The%20company%20says%20its%20compensation%20%26quot%3Breflects%20the%20cost%20of%20labor%20across%20several%20U.S.%20geographic%20markets.%26quot%3B%20Pay%20is%20based%20on%20market%20location%2C%20skills%2C%20knowledge%2C%20and%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20examples%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Area%20Manager%20II%20position%20based%20in%20Ohio%20with%20the%20option%20for%20virtual%20work%20has%20a%20pay%20range%20of%20%2461%2C400%20to%20%24100%2C000%20per%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Senior%20Project%20Manager%20role%20that's%20open%20to%20virtual%20candidates%20pays%20between%20%24121%2C000%20and%20%24235%2C200%20annually.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20virtual%20Operations%20Engineer%20annual%20salary%20ranges%20from%20%2448%2C600%20to%20%2493%2C500%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AmazonJobs%