20pretty%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20DRS%20credit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20has%20also%20been%20solid%20behind%20the%20stumps%2C%20and%20also%20has%20made%20a%20difference%20with%20his%20DRS%20judgements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20their%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Rahul's%20sharp%20judgment%20behind%20the%20stumps%20had%20earned%20them%20the%20prized-scalp%20of%20Dushmantha%20Chameera%20for%20a%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChameera%20had%20a%20faintest%20of%20touch%20as%20no%20fielder%20seemed%20to%20have%20appealed%20but%20Rahul%20after%20taking%20the%20catch%20was%20sure%20of%20an%20edge%20and%20convinced%20his%20skipper%20to%20take%20the%20DRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWicketkeeping%20gets%20difficult%20sometimes%2C%20but%20I%20enjoy%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20game%2C%20the%20bowlers%20have%20challenged%20me%20during%20DRS%20calls%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20give%20me%20enough%20credit%20(on%20DRS%20calls)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699868820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fovm7pst8_kl-rahul_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-dont-give-me-enough-credit-kl-rahuls-tongue-in-cheek-drs-remark-4568882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KL%20Rahul%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20form%20scoring%20the%20fastest%20century%20for%20India%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%2C%20was%20a%20relieved%20man%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-dont-give-me-enough-credit-kl-rahuls-tongue-in-cheek-drs-remark-4568882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-dont-give-me-enough-credit-kl-rahuls-tongue-in-cheek-drs-remark-4568882%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2