game%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kuldeep%20after%20India%20defeated%20the%20Netherlands%20by%20160%20runs%20to%20finish%20their%20league%20engagements%20on%20an%20all-win%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20yes%2C%20you%20need%20a%20couple%20of%20early%20wickets%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20the%20game%20and%20opponents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20will%20be%20a%20repeat%20of%20their%202019%20semifinal%20in%20Manchester%20which%20the%20Kiwis%20won%20by%2018%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kuldeep%20did%20not%20read%20too%20much%20into%20past%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%202019%20semifinals%20(against%20NZ)%20was%20four%20years%20ago.%20We%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20bilateral%20series%20after%20that%2C%20so%20we%20know%20the%20conditions%20(in%20India)%20and%20so%20do%20they.%20Our%20preparation%20has%20been%20good%20and%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20play%20good%20cricket%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20same%20vein%20in%20the%20next%20match%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20India's%20spin%20department%2C%20taking%2014%20wickets%20from%20nine%20matches%20at%20a%20fine%20economy%20rate%20of%204.15.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20down%20the%20pressures%20of%20a%20knockout%20match%2C%20Kuldeep%20said%20his%20focus%20would%20be%20on%20working%20on%20his%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20work%20on%20my%20rhythm%20and%20strengths%20and%20focus%20on%20how%20batsmen%20are%20trying%20to%20play%20me.%20My%20aim%20is%20to%20land%20the%20ball%20on%20the%20good%20length%20area%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20keep%20focusing%20on%20the%20process%20rather%20than%20on%20wickets.%20Hopefully%2C%20it%20will%20work%20in%20the%20next%20match%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98KL%20Rahul's%20impressive'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20return%20to%20top-flight%20cricket%20after%20a%20long%20injury%20lay-off%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20done%20well%20in%20his%20designated%20role%20as%20a%20wicket-keeper%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20fielding%20coach%20T%20Dilip%20lauded%20Rahul%20for%20making%20a%20wholehearted%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20doing%20truly%20amazing%20wicket-keeping%20at%20present.%20He%20came%20from%20a%20long%20injury%20layoff%2C%20so%2C%20that%20was%20really%20challenging.%20But%20he%20came%20up%20really%20well.%20He's%20someone%20who's%20been%20doing%20wicket-keeping%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20So%2C%20that%20is%20not%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI'm%20quite%20happy%20the%20way%20he%20is%20moving%20laterally.%20And%20also%2C%20for%20his%20height%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20the%20low%20catches%20which%20he%20is%20taking%20forward%20are%20outstanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dilip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699863840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8arq1v3o_kuldeep-and-rohit_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2F4-years-ago-india-star-revisits-old-wound-as-india-face-new-zealand-in-2019-world-cup-semi-final-rematch-4569199%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20India's%20spin%20department%2C%20taking%2014%20wickets%20from%20nine%20matches%20at%20a%20fine%20economy%20rate%20of%204.15.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2F4-years-ago-india-star-revisits-old-wound-as-india-face-new-zealand-in-2019-world-cup-semi-final-rematch-456919