ive%20chief%20ministers%20is%20an%20easy%20dodge%2C%20a%20massive%20distraction%20from%20the%20real%2C%20more%20prosaic%20question%20of%20just%20where%20the%20toxins%20are%20being%20released%2C%20how%20and%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20of%20nature%20carry%20no%20philosophy%2C%20make%20no%20judgments%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20sit%20down%20to%20write%20tracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20signed%20agreements%20to%20hand%20over%20national%20parks%20and%20swapping%20land%20assets%20to%20carbon%20emitting%20industrialists%2C%20after%20encouraging%20the%20production%20of%20more%20cars%20and%20chemicals%2C%20and%20hounding%20and%20harassing%20protesters%2C%20leaders%20cannot%20simply%20go%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20lotus%20pose%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20some%20holy%20river%20or%20%3Cem%3Ekund%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20within%20the%20womb%20room%20of%20an%20ancient%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20Ma%20Ganga%20and%20Ma%20Yamuna%20or%20Lord%20so-and-so%20give%20answers%20for%20the%20way%20out%20of%20extinction%20to%20leaders%20whose%20policies%20have%20ruined%20the%20source%20of%20our%20holiest%20rivers%20and%20temple%20towns%20in%20unimaginable%20ways%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENature%2C%20or%20Gods%20if%20you%20will%2C%20permit%20just%20so%20much%20cheating%20and%20exploitation%20of%20natural%20resources.%20No%20more.%20It%20is%20literally%20a%20pathetic%20fallacy%20to%20say%20that%20nature%20mourns%20extinction.%20Nature%20uses%20extinction%20to%20wipe%20off%20a%20species%20that%20has%20outlived%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20annual%20wearing%20of%20red%20poppies%20or%20Soldiers%E2%80%99%20Day%20flags%20upon%20our%20lapels%2C%20erecting%20war%20memorials%20to%20honour%20the%20dead%2C%20or%20showering%20pilgrims%20with%20rose%20petals%20and%20performing%20smoke-emitting%20%3Cem%3Eyagna%3C%2Fem%3Es%20for%20purifying%20the%20environment%20is%20not%20going%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20next%20mass%20extinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20hasten%20it.%3