was%20offered%20%3Cem%3Emakki%20ki%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20an%20Indian%20family%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Echapati%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread)%20made%20of%20flies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Bangkok%2C%20she%20was%20trained%20to%20use%20machine%20guns%2C%20how%20to%20hold%20and%20fire%20pistols%20at%20the%20enemy%2C%20learn%20the%20tactics%20of%20guerilla%20warfare%2C%20and%20how%20to%20drive%20a%20truck.%20She%20discovered%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20patriot%20fighting%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20a%20country%20she%20has%20no%20memories%20of%20but%20carries%20deep%20in%20her%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%201945%2C%20Asha%20became%20a%20lieutenant%20of%20the%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20Regiment%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%201945%2C%20Asha%20became%20a%20lieutenant%20of%20the%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20Regiment%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%