tors%2C%20occupational%20therapists%2C%20speech%20therapists%2C%20along%20with%20vocational%20training%2C%20physiotherapy%2C%20round%20the%20clock%20care%2C%20a%20mini-hospital%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%2C%20a%20nurse%20and%20an%20ambulance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20access%20to%20vast%20open%20areas%2C%20their%20residents%20participate%20in%20games%2C%20yoga%20and%20other%20activities%20with%20gusto.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20many%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20handle%20such%20children%2C%20often%20abandoning%20them.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20avenue%20for%20such%20children%20to%20really%20flourish%20and%20do%20their%20best.%20Parents%2C%20too%2C%20can%20be%20satisfied%20that%20their%20children%20are%20doing%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ravindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2062-year-old%20says%20that%20the%20initial%20few%20years%20of%20raising%20Akshay%20was%20challenging.%20He%20felt%20depressed%2C%20he%20admits%2C%20thinking%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20him%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20take%20care%20of%20him%20after%20us%3F%20This%20question%20plagues%20the%20mind%20of%20every%20parent%20of%20a%20disabled%20child.%20We%20have%20built%20this%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20that.%20I%20felt%20positive%20after%20building%20Sangopita.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20doing%20much%20better%20and%20has%20developed%20well%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20them%20wings%20to%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201498px)%20100vw%2C%201498px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%201498w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-300x176.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-500x293.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-768x450.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-150x88.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333895%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20children%20seem%20to%20have%20found%20their%20happy%20place%2C%20their%20parents%20describe%20Sangopita%20as%20a%20nurturing%20and%20thriving%20playground%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaj%20(16)%C2%A0%20has%20autism%20and%20is%20hyperactive%2C%20according%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20Swapna.%20A%20single%20mother%20who%20stays%20with%20her%20aged%20parents%2C%20she%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20look%20after%20him.%20Her%20parents%20weren%E2%80%99t%20equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20him%20when%20she%20went%20to%20work%20either.%20Raj%20was%20susceptible%20to%20getting%20fits%20as%20well.%20She%20found%20out%20about%20Sangopita%206%20years%20back%20and%20decided%20to%20enrol%20her%20son%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20doing%20much%20better%20and%20is%20happier%20there%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20about%20her%2C%20a%20mother%20who%20is%20staying%20away%20from%20her%20child%3F%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20my%20fate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20sadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20their%20parents%2C%20Sangeeta%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20manage%20her%20brother%20Rajiv%20Rao%2C%2034%2C%20who%20has%20a%20mental%20disability%2C%20when%20she%20went%20to%20work.%C2%A0